325
00:26:39,620 --> 00:26:40,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Aneh sekali.</font>

326
00:26:49,650 --> 00:26:50,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu.</font>

327
00:27:02,120 --> 00:27:03,290
<font color=#FFFF00>(Sung Hae Sung, SMA Chungho)</font>

328
00:27:04,490 --> 00:27:05,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Hae Sung?</font>

329
00:27:07,720 --> 00:27:08,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenal aku?</font>

330
00:27:09,850 --> 00:27:12,450
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, aku Hae Sung.
Aku Sung Hae Sung.</font>

331
00:27:12,690 --> 00:27:13,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenal aku 'kan?</font>

